Package: Schafr
Title: Single-Cell High-throughput Analysis Framework for RNA 5' End
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("ddxiaowu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ddxiaowu@example.com")
Description: An integrated R package for single-cell 5' RNA-seq analysis.
    Provides TSO filtering, 5' end counting (CTSS), parametric clustering 
    (paraclu algorithm implemented in pure R), ATAC-seq peak overlap filtering,
    and genomic annotation via ChIPseeker. Designed to replace the multi-step 
    shell/Python pipeline with a single R workflow.
